{"tid":1357961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦: 香港革命是長線的, 可能需要16年的時間","createTime":"2019-07-23T23:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T13:24:16.000Z","uid":134071,"like":149,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0631420568b29f7b7ec9898dc621737297083aec","tid":1357961,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:41:33.000Z","msg":"耐心是需要既. &nbsp;唔好因為花2年都無成果而心灰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20160814/s00022/1471137079445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20160814%2Fs00022%2F1471137079445&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=6dd5a39b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20160814%2Fs00022%2F1471137079445&h=c47195b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20160814/s00022/1471137079445</a><br />\n<br />\n什麼人訪問什麼人﹕梁天琦︰革命當然是長線的（文：Tam Daniel） (09:10)<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n譚︰呈請若失敗了，下一步是怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n梁︰這樣的話，就代表社會上全部方法用盡，都無法得到應有公義。好理性的結論就是，只有革命一條路，這是事實。問題只是怎樣去實現。我覺得我們做的工夫，<strong>都是沿着這條路去走︰影響社會，影響民心</strong>。這半年我覺得我們有一定的成績。<br />\n<br />\n譚︰這是兩種時間觀呢，革命和組織工作。<br />\n<br />\n梁︰革命當然是長線的，難道是一天半天嗎。辛亥革命固然指辛亥年發生的武昌起義，但我們更泛指多場起義，16年的時間。我和你講下星期會成功，或有一個確切的時間，一聽就知道是騙人啦。"},{"pid":"3e52192eeb183653bac996160d5a5498a7c57e47","tid":1357961,"uid":134071,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:42:37.000Z","msg":"(抗暴歷史) 匈牙利人發動勇武軍火革命, 33年後才成功<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1254175/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1254175/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"75e1b13d97c5997207e18982c96c8e7c2960e77f","tid":1357961,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:43:30.000Z","msg":"心理準備好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi